{"word":"Plague","slug":"plague","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Plague</b> As a judgment on the Egyptians:<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=105'>Psa 105</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=135&verse=9'>Psa 135:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=7&verse=36'>Act 7:36</a> <br/> - The plague of blood<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=7&verse=25'>Exo 7:25</a> <br/> - The plague of frogs<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=8&verse=15'>Exo 8:15</a> <br/> - The plague of lice<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=8&verse=19'>Exo 8:19</a> <br/> - The plague of flies<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=8&verse=20'>Exo 8:20</a> <br/> - The plague on cattle<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=9&verse=7'>Exo 9:7</a> <br/> - The plague of boils and blains<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=9&verse=12'>Exo 9:12</a> <br/> - The plague of hail<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=9&verse=34'>Exo 9:34</a> <br/> - The plague of locusts<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=10&verse=20'>Exo 10:20</a> <br/> - The plague of darkness<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=10&verse=23'>Exo 10:23</a> <br/> - The plague of death of the firstborn<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=11&verse=7'>Exo 11:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=12&verse=17'>Exo 12:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=12&verse=30'>Exo 12:30</a> <br/> As a judgment on the Israelites:<br/> - On account of idolatry<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=32&verse=35'>Exo 32:35</a> <br/> - After eating quail<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=11&verse=33'>Num 11:33</a> <br/> - After refusing to enter the promised land<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=14&verse=37'>Num 14:37</a> <br/> - After murmuring on account of the destruction of Korah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=16&verse=50'>Num 16:50</a> <br/> - The plague of serpents<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=21&verse=6'>Num 21:6</a> <br/> - For the sin of Peor<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=22&verse=17'>Jos 22:17</a> <br/> - On account of David's sin<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=24&verse=25'>2Sa 24:25</a> <br/> As a judgment on the Philistines<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=6&verse=5'>1Sa 6:5</a><br/> Denounced as a judgment<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=26&verse=21'>Lev 26:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=28&verse=59'>Deu 28:59</a><br/> Foretold<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=11&verse=6'>Rev 11:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=15&verse=1'>Rev 15:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=15&verse=8'>Rev 15:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=16'>Rev 16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=22&verse=19'>Rev 22:19</a><br/><a href='S:Judgments'>Judgments</a>; <a href='S:Pestilence'>Pestilence</a>"}]}